Stack, naming, and universal conventions are in this file.
For section work: **sections.mdc** applies automatically (globs `src/components/sections/**`, `src/types/sections.ts`).
For ACF/normalizer work: **acf.mdc** applies automatically (globs `src/lib/acf/**`, `acf-import-bundle.json`).
For WP REST work: **wordpress.mdc** applies automatically (globs `src/lib/wordpress/**`, `src/app/api/**`).
For type-only work: **types.mdc** applies automatically (globs `src/types/**`).
Do **NOT** read `ai-context.md` — it is deprecated in favour of these scoped rules.

---

## Project summary

Salonora is a **multilingual (nl/en) Next.js 15 App Router** marketing site that renders **WordPress** content: ACF flexible sections, pages, posts, CPTs (`service`, `testimonial`, `case_study`), globals (header/footer/options), **Yoast** metadata, **Polylang** locales, and **Contact Form 7**. The repo includes **OMB headless** PHP (`wordpress/`: theme, plugin, mu-plugin) aligned with the Next fetchers.

