## Naming conventions

| Thing                | Convention    | Example                          |
| -------------------- | ------------- | -------------------------------- |
| ACF layout key       | snake_case    | `split_copy_framed`            |
| Section type literal | snake_case    | `type: "split_copy_framed"`    |
| Section TS type      | PascalCase + SectionT | `SplitCopyFramedSectionT` |
| Component folder     | kebab-case    | `split-copy-framed/`           |
| Component export     | PascalCase    | `SplitCopyFramedSection`       |
| Field mapper keys    | snake_case    | `row.badge_text`                 |
| ACF JSON field keys  | `field_omb_[layout]_*` | `field_omb_split_copy_framed_title` |

