## Animation classes

```ts
// src/lib/animation-classes.ts
export const REVEAL_ITEM = "reveal-item";
```

- Apply `className={REVEAL_ITEM}` (or the string `"reveal-item"`) to elements that should animate on scroll.
- Picked up by GSAP scroll observers in `src/components/animations/` (page-level `PageScrollAnimations`).
- Do not invent other animation class names — `REVEAL_ITEM` is the only defined constant.
- GSAP animations that need client interactivity require `"use client"` on the component.

